    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
