    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the spaghetti is cooking, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Wipe out the reserved pan and return to a medium heat with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> sliced shallot </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p>",
