    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Once the shallot has softened, add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 4-5 min over a medium-high heat or until the tomatoes have softened</p>",
