      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Trapanese-style pesto spaghetti</strong> topped with the <strong>homemade stracciatella</strong> and <strong>herby breadcrumbs</strong></p><p>Serve with<strong> </strong>the <strong>salad</strong> to the side and top with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
